{"tid":306830,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"暝想嗰時個腦係諗緊咩","createTime":"2017-07-03T00:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T12:41:26.000Z","uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81a4032385ff9f57db3c2dac3b42e88bdb3795f0","tid":306830,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:39:29.000Z","msg":"懷疑自己有焦慮導致胃病<br />\n嘗試吓暝想放鬆自己<br />\n注意自己嘅呼吸<br />\n點先算係正確嘅暝想呢？個腦應該處於咩狀態？<br />\n做左陣覺得自己似釣魚多過暝想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322efbd35b6ddf02df8508870ed7512c52695a06","tid":306830,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:45:19.000Z","msg":"冥想<br />\n<br />\n搵人教唔好亂做"},{"pid":"4aee431a0dca89f651e2e5b0d869e5c420ab3e3e","tid":306830,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:35:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冥想<br />\n<br />\n搵人教唔好亂做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解一定要搵人教？"},{"pid":"77e15e3733e25cfc320eebe15be04cfbe0d367f2","tid":306830,"uid":113675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T05:38:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>懷疑自己有焦慮導致胃病<br />\n嘗試吓暝想放鬆自己<br />\n注意自己嘅呼吸<br />\n點先算係正確嘅暝想呢？個腦應該處於咩狀態？<br />\n做左陣覺得自己似釣魚多過暝想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實做meditation無話應該要有正確既狀態<br />\n會分心諗野好正常<br />\n只要慢慢帶返注意力去自己度已經無問題<br />\n<br />\n利申有試過做<br />\n有帶過人做"},{"pid":"feba4507625cd5ce1b7000378aa19660a3d4cc8e","tid":306830,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T09:54:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冥想<br />\n<br />\n搵人教唔好亂做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解一定要搵人教？</blockquote><br />\n見過幾條new age撚自學，跟住開始見到&hellip;&hellip;嘢<br />\n要護咗身先同搵人引導，所以要有人帶<br />\n唔係隻隻練法都係咁，但唔知你學邊隻"},{"pid":"b373c2b3ed33649e7b5b438fc148a78562dd8b52","tid":306830,"uid":55296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:26:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冥想<br />\n<br />\n搵人教唔好亂做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解一定要搵人教？</blockquote><br />\n見過幾條new age撚自學，跟住開始見到&hellip;&hellip;嘢<br />\n要護咗身先同搵人引導，所以要有人帶<br />\n唔係隻隻練法都係咁，但唔知你學邊隻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想舒緩緊張咋"},{"pid":"d34005fb501cec5fce8fa1faf5fb8e1bb44d6cdc","tid":306830,"uid":63867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:28:58.000Z","msg":"可以諗呼吸 分散注意力<br />\n留意自己嘅一呼一吸<br />\n每淡氣既味道，濕潤，流通"},{"pid":"8dea4d69485857429ee9186f1c7778999e322007","tid":306830,"uid":78793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:29:49.000Z","msg":"我自從冥想左一次後個靈力感強左好多，成日feel到有野，搞到我而家成日都會驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時候仲會唔小心入左冥想狀態屌，一入我就要即刻分心，因為唔想feel到有野唉"},{"pid":"30ac86c3732a46f88cddfe098f1b8ee9aa8602ec","tid":306830,"uid":78793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:31:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自從冥想左一次後個靈力感強左好多，成日feel到有野，搞到我而家成日都會驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時候仲會唔小心入左冥想狀態屌，一入我就要即刻分心，因為唔想feel到有野唉</blockquote><br />\n同堆我第一次真正冥想果時係感受到能量流係我體內，真係有股能量由下而上流動。"},{"pid":"0c8865358560f237222cf8b437f24894447a1ffc","tid":306830,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T11:21:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自從冥想左一次後個靈力感強左好多，成日feel到有野，搞到我而家成日都會驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時候仲會唔小心入左冥想狀態屌，一入我就要即刻分心，因為唔想feel到有野唉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以講詳細啲"},{"pid":"3b2a24730dbcbe24a40760c8cfa5173e5b884358","tid":306830,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T11:28:07.000Z","msg":"數下呼吸囉，唔使太強求，你都係想放鬆"},{"pid":"1924f63a38ca40732e318195f858cc31e6492dac","tid":306830,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T12:04:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>數下呼吸囉，唔使太強求，你都係想放鬆</blockquote><br />\n依家就係深呼吸數五秒，呼氣數五秒咁"},{"pid":"fc0d6f073adda4fd4a1f09864df11640ff5de2cf","tid":306830,"uid":113675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T12:33:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>數下呼吸囉，唔使太強求，你都係想放鬆</blockquote><br />\n依家就係深呼吸數五秒，呼氣數五秒咁</blockquote><br />\n其實咁樣就唔算係做到自然<br />\nMeditation本來就係要自然咁呼吸<br />\n無需要特登控制節奏"},{"pid":"46a9a78e730374f05b8fc6d001e7c0141d6f86a2","tid":306830,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T12:41:26.000Z","msg":"撞鬼唔好喊"}]}